Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a big moment for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you call a silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, that's Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} had always been\Nprotecting this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's the silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Oden Wouldn't Be Oden If It Wasn't Boiled!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We were being protected by Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you tell us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard to swallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know the truth about Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukurokuju!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth only creates turmoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"The silly lord who rebelled against the Shogun dies."\NThat's what people will think,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the execution will be over soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this execution is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew the consequences, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already sharing the same fate with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}'s retainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys became Orochi's dogs,\Nso I'm not gonna obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} and the others,\NI'll die with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We'll all survive\Nand take you guys down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shogun Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Please!\N--I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They need treatment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only the Shogun's family,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but all the common people\Npersecuted the Kurozumi Clan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The people instantly realized how dreadful\Nits vengeful descendant Orochi could be.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the reason behind Oden's strange behavior\Nof dancing naked for five years,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}spread among the people in no time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the person who saved us that day was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet we mocked him so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was enduring\Nmore than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We're a bunch of fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone rushed to Oden.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They finally realized that\Nthe protracted execution they were witnessing...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...involving this man who was facing death\Nin front of their eyes...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was the only hope for the Land of Wano!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}, you must survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for cursing you\Nwithout knowing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for protecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're such brown-nosers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So straightforward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, Orochi, of course,\Nwouldn't leave the people's excitement be,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and before they knew it, they were surrounded by\NKaido and Orochi's armed subordinates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The temperature of the oil surpassed\N700 degrees Celsius and kept rising.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't concede!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arrows carried messages\Nto the castle in each region to publicize the incident.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,KURI   KIBI   FLOWER   RINGO\NUDON   HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,HAKUMAI, LAND OF WANO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Land of Wano's letter-arrows\Ncan travel a great distance...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I manage to survive this boiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to open up this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're talking about something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking about opening up before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the isolation is deeply tied to Kozuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you find at sea\Nwhere you traveled with Roger and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those responsible for isolating this country\Nfrom the rest of the world a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...were the Kozuki Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect the Land of Wano from an enormous force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...awaits a certain figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When that figure shows up after 800 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,this country must be welcoming\Nand cooperative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...definitely kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can really survive this boiling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One third of the time has already passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikunojo!\NLet's hear what Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is like hell\Nwhere even the heat is lethal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boiling oil is cooking Oden.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hasn't he died yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Raise the temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the oil boil more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat can't kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll set out on a great adventure\Nbeyond your wildest imagination!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My little brother!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight! Seven! Six! Five! Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He survived the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...withstood the boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--He really did it!\N--Remarkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}'s victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-sama's name has been cleared, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the whole country is on our side again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for it, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease him, stupid cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He surely won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't speak so idly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to set all of us free\Nif we survived for an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I conceived of the idea of changing his sentence\Nfrom boiling to shooting a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll execute not only Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but also all his family members!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a childish excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what you said!\NOden-{\i1}sama{\i} did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have a problem,\Nshow yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pump lead into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! To Kuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an interesting conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after them!\NEliminate the name Kozuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your body is already "dead" anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the least I could do for you...\NI'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozuki's era will end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate my samurai retainers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop eating, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I give up! I give up! I give up!\NI thought you were a dead person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools who grew up pampered in the capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...can't understand\Nwhat it feels like to live in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanna say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you, you pricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you bully those little ones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you lend people money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, go steal food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A Daimyo shouldn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you act miserably now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,people will talk about how heroically you died\Nfor generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...being forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...my spirit will live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so upright of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Build your strength while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...if people talk about me over a drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:32.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,I'M HAPPY IF PEOPLE TALK ABOUT ME OVER A DRINK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My samurai retainers!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toki!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momonosuke!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiyori!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm off!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oden{\i} wouldn't be {\i1}oden{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ODEN{\i} WOULDN'T BE {\i1}ODEN{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...if it wasn't boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:42.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,IF IT WASN'T BOILED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raided by Kaido, Oden Castle is set alight!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After repeated attacks,\Nthe Kozuki Clan has nowhere left to run.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even cornered, Toki still struggles to save\NOden's dream and the country's future!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Believing the sun will rise, she makes a fervent wish\Nand entrusts the fate of the Land of Wano to others.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Castle on Fire! The Fate of the Kozuki Clan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
